        <p id="Par30">We also calculated PVE using the mixed model (Eq. (<xref rid="Equ3" ref-type="">3</xref>)) without <italic>β</italic><sub>1</sub> and <italic>β</italic><sub>2</sub> as follows:<list list-type="order"><list-item><p id="Par31">Calculated single PVE<sub>self</sub> or single PVE<sub>nei</sub> by setting either <inline-formula id="IEq60"><alternatives><tex-math id="M127">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
