      <p id="Par46">To estimate PVE<sub>self</sub> and PVE<sub>nei</sub>, we applied a linear mixed model (Eq. (<xref rid="Equ3" ref-type="">3</xref>)) to the leaf damage score data for the field-grown <italic>A. thaliana</italic>. The leaf damage variation was significantly explained by the single PVE<sub>self</sub> that represented additive genetic variation (single PVE<sub>self</sub> = 0.173, <inline-formula id="IEq72"><alternatives><tex-math id="M151">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
